cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper discusses reinforcement learning algorithms and their comparison in terms of the expressive power of neural networks for policies, Q-functions, and dynamics. This topic falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of model-based planning, which is relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper applies the proposed algorithm to MuJoCo benchmark tasks, which are related to neural networks (cs.NE).
